    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
