            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While everything's in the oven, add the<strong> remaining soy sauce </strong>to a plate with your<strong> basa fillet[s]</strong></p><p>Turn the <strong>basa</strong> several times until the soy sauce fully soaks into the fish</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>cornflour </strong>all over and rub it into both sides of the fish until fully coated – this is your <strong>coated basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Coat the fish in the cornflour one side at a time to avoid stickiness!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1-1657546104815-x200.jpg",
