            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>crispy soy basa</strong> to a plate and return the pan to a medium heat</p><p>Add the<strong> sesame butter mix </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until it starts to thicken</p><p>Once thickened, remove the pan from the heat and add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> – this is your <strong>sesame, honey & lime sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Not a fan of lime? Just add a little!</p>",
