            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy soy basa </strong>with the <strong>sticky wedges & roasted pepper</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>sesame, honey & lime sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
